
    -o]-[Where & When]-[o-


TRSAC'00.5 will take place on 
"Bankagerskolen" in Horsens, Denmark 
the 3rd-5th November 2000.

Transport
------------

By train/bus:
Take the train to Horsens. From the 
train/bus-station in Horsens take bus 
no. 5 towards "Bankager" and ask the 
driver to stop at "Bankagerskolen" 
(right after the roundabout and 
"Føtex").

By car:
Take highway E45 to Horsens. Get off 
the highway towards "Horsens S" 
(offramp no. 57) and turn towards 
Horsens (just check the sign). Go
straight through all roundabouts until 
you reach a trafficlight. Turn left.

At the second trafficlight turn right 
and take the first road to the left. 
This is "Bankagervej". Follow the 
road. Just after the roundabout you'll 
see "Føtex". Now you should check for 
TRSAC signs leading you the rest of 
the way. They're on the right hand 
side just after "Føtex".

A roadmap is availiable at 
www.cromatics.dk/trsac/

if this seems unreasonable, do not 
hesitate to contact us a
booster@cromatics.dk

Entrance Fee
------------

The entrance fee is 50dkr for danes. 
Foreigners except matt/ozone get in
for free ;o)

Rules
------------

Excessive drinking combined with 
loud, noisy and disturbing behaviour
will not be tolerated.

If such behaviour takes place you 
will be subject to one or more of the
following treatments:

1. Nic0 will sell ya one if his 
   special "choker-wieners".
2. Farfar beats ya with a 
   cotton-stick!
3. You have to mud-wrestle Darkhawk!
4. We will leave you outside, naked 
   and unarmed, alone with the violent
   youth in Denmark!

Legal notice
------------

1. We take NO responsibility for any 
   broken/stolen equipment at TRSAC 
   including damage caused by 
   powerfailure.

2. If you break anything you'll have 
   to pay for it.

3. If you break a window in a car or 
   set fire to the floor you will get
   only 66.6% of your duck.

4. If any matters arise at all we will 
   only meet your demand if threatened 
   by a lawsuit!

5. Btw, it's unfair to threaten us!

6. We WILL whine if threatened by a 
   lawyer!

(3 - 6 inspired by The Party)

